      "description": "Hey there! I'm honestly so sad to let this beauty go, but it\u2019s time for someone else to enjoy it! This car is in absolutely incredible shape\u2014honestly, you\u2019d think it just rolled off the showroom floor. It\u2019s been pampered since day one and looks and drives like a total dream. If you\u2019re looking for something that\u2019s basically brand new without the new-car price tag, this is definitely the one for you! Feel free to reach out with any questions!",
