    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offered is an investment-grade 2004 BMW M3 (E46) Coupe, finished in Alpine White over Cinnamon Nappa leather. This example is powered by the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six, featuring individual throttle bodies and a 7,900 RPM redline, mated to a precise Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox. Mechanical integrity is paramount: the dual-VANOS system has been overhauled with Beisan components, and the rear subframe has been proactively reinforced to ensure long-term structural rigidity. The chassis retains its factory-tuned poise with a functional M Variable Differential Lock and original Style 67 forged wheels. This vehicle exhibits zero signs of typical interior delamination or bolster wear, representing a turn-key opportunity for the discerning collector seeking the peak of naturally aspirated M-division performance.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 40
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_9_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_9",
