      "description": "Presented in impeccable, showroom-standard condition, this vehicle represents the pinnacle of its class. Meticulously maintained and showing no signs of wear, it offers an unrivaled driving experience for the discerning collector or enthusiast. Every surface and mechanical component reflects a standard of care rarely seen on the secondary market. We invite serious inquiries to appreciate this exceptional example in person.",
      "price": 46500.0,
