    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m honestly a little sad to see this beauty go, but it\u2019s time for it to find a new home. This car has been my absolute pride and joy\u2014it's been pampered, garage-kept, and is in such stunning shape that it still feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor! If you're looking for a ride that's literally flawless and drives like a dream, you've found it. I\u2019ve taken care of every little detail so you can just hop in and enjoy the ride. Come check it out, I promise you\u2019re going to love it!",
      "price": 43500.0,
