    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Available is an investment-grade E46 M3, featuring the legendary S54B32 high-revving straight-six with individual throttle bodies. This specimen boasts a structurally sound chassis with proactive subframe reinforcement and a comprehensive service history addressing all critical S54 failure points. The double-VANOS system has been overhauled with precision Beisan components, and the rod bearings were replaced with VAC Motorsports coated shells to ensure internal longevity. Power is delivered through a tactile 6-speed manual transmission to a variable M differential lock, providing exceptional mechanical grip. The suspension retains its factory-spec kinematics with fresh bushings and Sachs dampers, offering the precise, communicative feedback synonymous with the M-division. The exterior maintains a deep, swirl-free luster, while the cockpit features pristine Nappa leather with zero bolster compression. This is a mechanically synchronized, turn-key example for the discerning collector.",
